## Vector addition problem
## Part 1
## By K. Kurz, Kurz@NSRL31.NSRL.ROCHESTER.EDU
## Imported Files:
## ${CAPA_Tools}Problem
## Values needing defined:
## prob_val (number, e.g. /LET prob_val=1)
